{
  "text": "All Fjme plasmids coding for streptomycin resistance also conferred resistance to spectinomycin, whereas the independent group 2 SSu resistance determinants do not code for spectinomycin resistance (see text). 1974-5 1974 1975 1970 1973 1976 1969-74t 1974 1971-4 1975 1976 1974 1971 1975 1974 1973 1975 1972 1974 Autotransferring covalently bonded to form single plasmids which transferred intact and remained transferable from their new hosts (Anderson, 19686, 1969; [CITATION_1] .",
